OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779753774
OL,3,CPoorer drivers more likely to miss out
OL,4,Con car finance payouts, lawyers say
OL,6,FLow-income drivers who relied on a
OL,7,Floan for cheaper cars are more likely
OL,8,Fto miss out on payouts under the UK
OL,9,Fwatchdog's plans for compensation,
OL,10,Faccording to new analysis.
OL,12,FAround 1.1 million low-value car
OL,13,Ffinance agreements will not be
OL,14,Feligible for redress through the
OL,15,FFinancial Conduct Authority's (FCA)
OL,16,Fscheme, analysis by consumer law firm
OL,17,FSlater and Gordon found.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
