CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779753774
OL,3,CPoorer drivers more likely to miss out
OL,4,Con car finance payouts, lawyers say
OL,6,FThis is because car finance deals
OL,7,Finvolving smaller amounts of
OL,8,Fcommission ` #120 or less for
OL,9,Fagreements before April 1 2014, and
OL,10,F#150 or less for after that date ` are
OL,11,Fconsidered to be fair and are not
OL,12,Feligible for compensation under the
OL,13,Ffinal rules of the scheme.
OL,15,FThe FCA said commission amounts below
OL,16,Fthese levels are unlikely to have
OL,17,Finfluenced the consumers' decision or
OL,18,Fbroker's behaviour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779753774
OL,3,CPoorer drivers more likely to miss out
OL,4,Con car finance payouts, lawyers say
OL,6,FBut Slater and Gordon said in the
OL,7,Fmajority of cases where smaller
OL,8,Famounts were borrowed, often a few
OL,9,Fthousand pounds or less, the loan was
OL,10,Fused to buy cheaper cars or vans.
OL,12,FThis indicates that it
OL,13,Fdisproportionately impacts more
OL,14,Ffinancially stretched consumers, as
OL,15,Fopposed to loans being used as a top-
OL,16,Fup for more expensive vehicles.
OL,18,FThe firm used its own client data and
OL,19,Fcase experience to establish the
OL,20,Fpattern.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
