OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779753774
OL,3,CPoorer drivers more likely to miss out
OL,4,Con car finance payouts, lawyers say
OL,6,FThe FCA set up the industry-wide
OL,7,Fscheme to compensate people who were
OL,8,Fmis-sold a car loan between April 2007
OL,9,Fand November 2024 because of "hidden"
OL,10,Fcommission that motorists were not
OL,11,Fproperly informed about when they made
OL,12,Fthe agreement.
OL,14,FSlater and Gordon argues that the
OL,15,Fminimum commission threshold
OL,16,Fautomatically rules out agreements
OL,17,Fthat may have been unfair, while also
OL,18,Foverlooking the fact that relatively
OL,19,Fsmall sums can make a material
OL,20,Fdifference to poorer households.
OL,26,@qD@^OUqD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
