OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779753774
OL,3,CPoorer drivers more likely to miss out
OL,4,Con car finance payouts, lawyers say
OL,6,FElizabeth Comley, the law firm's chief
OL,7,Foperating officer, said: "The people
OL,8,Fbeing cut out of this scheme are those
OL,9,Fat the lower end of the market `
OL,10,Fdrivers who borrowed smaller amounts
OL,11,Fto buy cheaper cars and who can least
OL,12,Fafford to lose out.
OL,14,F"You don't see high-income consumers
OL,15,Ftaking out #2,000 car finance
OL,16,Fagreements.
OL,18,F"These are people stretching to afford
OL,19,Fa vehicle, and they are now being told
OL,20,Fthey don't qualify for compensation."
OL,26,@oD@ZOUvD@AOUzD@AOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
