OL,3,CPoorer drivers more likely to miss out
OL,4,Con car finance payouts, lawyers say
OL,6,FConsumer Voice, a group representing
OL,7,Fconsumers, is pursuing a legal
OL,8,Fchallenge to the planned compensation
OL,9,Fpackage which it argues will short-
OL,10,Fchange drivers who suffered harm when
OL,11,Fthey took out a loan.
OL,13,FBut the regulator is also facing a
OL,14,Flawsuit from three lenders ` the
OL,15,Ffinancial services arms of carmakers
OL,16,FVolkswagen and Mercedes-Benz and the
OL,17,Fcar finance arm of French bank Credit
OL,18,FAgricole ` who are not happy with the
OL,19,Fredress plans that are set to cost the
OL,20,Findustry some #9.1 billion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
