CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779753774
OL,3,CPoorer drivers more likely to miss out
OL,4,Con car finance payouts, lawyers say
OL,6,FThe legal battle means the scheme is
OL,7,Fcurrently in limbo with millions of
OL,8,Fpayouts hanging in the balance, as the
OL,9,FFCA warned over delays, changes or the
OL,10,Fpotential for it to collapse.
OL,12,FDespite the uncertainty of the legal
OL,13,Fcases, the watchdog has said it will
OL,14,Fdefend its scheme which it says is
OL,15,F"fair to consumers and proportionate
OL,16,Ffor firms".
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
