CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779753774
OL,3,CPoorer drivers more likely to miss out
OL,4,Con car finance payouts, lawyers say
OL,6,FIt is still advising consumers to
OL,7,Fcomplain directly to their lender if
OL,8,Fthey think they might be owed
OL,9,Fcompensation, and has repeatedly said
OL,10,Fthey do not need to use a law firm or
OL,11,Fclaims management company which can
OL,12,Fcharge unnecessary fees.
OL,14,FThe FCA has been contacted for comment
OL,15,Fon Slater and Gordon's analysis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
